Readme
======

This is a simple example of using Flask, CoffeeScript and jQuery to make and handle AJAX
requests.


Running the example
-------------------

To run the example, Python must be installed with the Flask library.

Run in your favourite terminal (or command prompt for windows users):

$ python app.py

Now visit localhost:5000 with your favourite web browser.

Note: JavaScript must be enabled on your browser for the example to work.
